      • CspClientCredentialsSecurityContext

        public CspClientCredentialsSecurityContext(java.lang.String clientId,
                                           char[] clientSecret,
                                           java.lang.String orgId)
        Parameters:
        clientId - Client Identifier (AKA App ID) for CSP; must not be null
        clientSecret - Client Secret (AKA App Secret) for CSP; must not be null
        orgId - Organization ID for which access token needs to be generated. If this is null, token will be generated for default orgId.
